w'; font-size:11pt; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt 83.6pt; padding-left:6.25pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">Daily conference calls or video conferencing</span></li><li style="font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:11pt; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt 83.6pt; padding-left:6.25pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">Regular meetings of </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">snow cells and teams</span></li></ul><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt 46.06pt; padding-left:7.94pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">Wider briefings and information disseminated via company intranets and e-mail, for staff who are not directly involved, but must remain well informed</span></li><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt 46.06pt; padding-left:7.94pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">Development of a new stakeholder extranet</span></li><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt 46.06pt; padding-left:7.94pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">Use of flight disruption coordination teams</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt"> comprising representatives from all major stakeholders on the airport</span></li><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt 46.06pt; padding-left:7.94pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">Development of real-time situational awareness mapping</span></li><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt 46.06pt; padding-left:7.94pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">Installation of additional CCTV views</span></li><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt 46.06pt; padding-l