t-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt 46.06pt; padding-left:7.94pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">Airlines liaising directly with Airport Control Centre as single point of contact</span></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom-color:#4bacc6; border-bottom-style:solid; border-bottom-width:1pt; border-left-color:#4bacc6; border-left-style:solid; border-left-width:1pt; border-right-color:#4bacc6; border-right-style:solid; border-right-width:1pt; border-top-color:#4bacc6; border-top-style:solid; border-top-width:1pt; padding-left:5.4pt; padding-right:5.4pt; vertical-align:top; width:127.6pt"><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 17.85pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">Winter Runway Assessment Trial</span></p></td><td style="border-bottom-color:#4bacc6; border-bottom-style:solid; border-bottom-width:1pt; border-left-color:#4bacc6; border-left-style:solid; border-left-width:1pt; border-right-color:#4bacc6; border-right-style:solid; border-right-width:1pt; border-top-color:#4bacc6; border-top-style:solid; border-top-width:1pt; padding-left:5.4pt; padding-right:5.4pt; vertical-align:top; width:354.6pt"><ul type="disc" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt 46.06pt; padding-left:7.94pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">A number of airports are also participating in the CAA Evaluation of UK Winter Runway Assessment Trial</span></li></ul></td></tr></table><p style="margin:0pt"><br style="page-break-before:always; clear:both" /></p><table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="border-collapse:collapse; margin-left:0pt; width:482.2pt"><tr style="height:66.3pt"><td style="background-color:#000000; border-bottom-color:#4bacc6; border-bottom-style:solid; border-bottom-width:2.25pt; border-left-color:#4bacc6; border-left-style:solid; border-left-width:1pt; border-right-color:#4bacc